3.webm?t=1677222576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123450/extras/c60cc86d4523eae3da500c7a72d8b373.mp4?t=1677222576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use this ability to dodge attacks and dash to overcome platforming challenges. Armed with a sword and revolver you'll need to perform combo kills to reload and chase the highest scores and rankings.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123450/extras/1e992915419298ae1db4f760c89e25cb.poster.avif?t=1677222576\" width=480 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123450/extras/1e992915419298ae1db4f760c89e25cb.webm?t=1677222576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123450/extras/1e992915419298ae1db4f760c89e25cb.mp4?t=1677222576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Kill all who oppose you as you rampage through the city to discover who betrayed you and why. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123450/extras/df23ccbc74ed12ccb0f2d471d0784377.poster.avif?t=1677222576\" width=480 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123450/extras/df23ccbc74ed12ccb0f2d471d0784377.webm?t=1677222576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123450/extras/df23ccbc74ed12ccb0f2d471d0784377.mp4?t=1677222576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Trust no one, kill them all.",
